.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-5::.
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, avocado, peas, corn
4 different pets are kept: cat, dog, hedgehog, pony
1. the person eating peas is not the owner of the hedgehog##6
2. the owner of the cat and the person eating pomegranate have different parity positions##9
3. the owner of the dog and the person eating avocado have different parity positions##9
4. the owner of the dog is somewhere to the left of the person eating peas##5
5. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person eating corn##1
6. the person eating avocado is not the owner of the dog##6
7. the person eating corn is somewhere to the left of the person eating avocado##5
8. the owner of the cat is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
9. the owner of the pony is not the person eating corn##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | pomegranate | peas | corn  | avocado |
| Pet           | dog   | cat     | hedgehog | pony      |

