.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, water, milk, lemonade
There are 4 different nationalities: american, brazilian, indian, thai
1. the person drinking water is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person drinking milk is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the indian is somewhere to the left of the person drinking lemonade##5
4. the american and the person drinking milk have the same parity positions##9
5. the person drinking lemonade and the american have different parity positions##9
6. the indian is not to the left of the person drinking sprite##8
7. the thai is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
8. the person drinking water is not to the right of the thai##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | water | sprite | milk | lemonade |
| Nationality   | thai        | indian    | american   | brazilian |

