.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-9::.
City: miami, paris, venice, new-york
4 different pets are kept: fish, hamster, mouse, rabbit
1. the person traveling to miami is somewhere between the owner of the fish and the owner of the hamster##7
2. the owner of the hamster is not to the right of the owner of the rabbit##8
3. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
5. the person traveling to paris is not the owner of the fish##6
6. the person traveling to venice is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to paris##5
7. the person traveling to new-york and the owner of the rabbit have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby   | new-york | paris | miami | venice |
| Pet     | hamster     | mouse     | rabbit     | fish    |

