.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-10::.
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, papaya, pepper, watermelon
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, sudoku, gardening, fishing
1. the person who's hobby is fishing is not to the left of the person eating broccoli##8
2. the person eating watermelon and the person who's hobby is fishing have the same parity positions##9
3. the person who's hobby is sudoku is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is gardening##5
4. the person eating pepper is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
5. the person eating papaya is somewhere between the person who's hobby is sudoku and the person who's hobby is fishing##7
6. the person eating watermelon is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Food        | pepper | broccoli   | papaya | watermelon |
| Transport   | gardening   | sudoku | board-games    | fishing      |

