3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the chaman-smoker##1
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the havana-smoker have different parity positions##9
5. the vegafina-smoker is on the right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
