2. the person who likes blood-red is not to the left of the person driving the trike##8
3. the person who likes grey and the person driving the helicopter have the same parity positions##9
4. the person driving the trike is the person who likes grey##1
5. the person who likes coral is somewhere to the right of the person driving the bike##5
6. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who likes grey##1

.:: Answer ::.
