.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-13::.
There 4 different types of food: garlic, lemon, nectarine, peach
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, light-blue, coral, orange
1. the person eating peach is not the person who likes orange##6
2. the person who likes orange is not to the right of the person who likes blue##8
3. the person eating nectarine is not to the left of the person eating peach##8
4. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the person eating lemon##3
5. the person eating peach is on the left or right of the person who likes coral##3
6. the person who likes orange is on the far left##1
7. the person who likes blue is on the left of the person eating nectarine##1
8. the person eating garlic is the person who likes light-blue##1
9. the person eating peach and the person who likes blue have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | lemon   | peach    | nectarine | garlic    |
| Nationality   | orange | blue | coral   | light-blue |

