.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-16::.
4 different games are played: bridge, chess, backgammon, whist
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: comedy, crime, family, mystery
1. the person watching comedy movies is not the person playing whist##6
2. the person playing whist is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
4. the person watching crime movies is in an odd position##4
5. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
6. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person playing chess##1
7. the person playing chess is somewhere to the right of the person playing whist##5
8. the person watching comedy movies and the person playing bridge have the same parity positions##9
9. the person watching family movies and the person playing backgammon have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage      | whist   | chess  | backgammon  | bridge |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | family | mystery | comedy      |

