House: cottage, craftsman, cape-cod, palace
1. the writer and the cottage house have the same parity positions##9
2. the cape-cod house is on the left of the craftsman house##1
3. the security-guard is not to the right of the cottage house##8
4. the writer is not to the right of the freelancer##8
5. the cottage house is in an even position##4
6. the cape-cod house and the electrician have the same parity positions##9
7. the cottage house and the security-guard have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|       |      1      |   2    |     3      |       4        |
| Job   | electrician | writer | freelancer | security-guard |
| Pet   | cape-cod    | craftsman   | palace        | cottage            |

