.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-9-20::.
4 different pets are kept: mouse, ferret, rat, goat
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, fishing, magic-tricks, reading
 1. the owner of the goat is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 2. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 3. the person who's hobby is reading is not to the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##8
 4. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an odd position##4
 5. the person who's hobby is board-games is not the owner of the ferret##6
 6. the owner of the goat is not to the right of the owner of the mouse##8
 7. the owner of the goat and the person who's hobby is fishing have the same parity positions##9
 8. the owner of the ferret is not to the right of the owner of the rat##8
 9. the owner of the goat is the person who's hobby is fishing##1
10. the owner of the ferret and the person who's hobby is fishing have the same parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |      2       |    3    |      4      |
| Beverage   | ferret    | rat        | goat   | mouse      |
| Hobby      | reading | magic-tricks | fishing | board-games |

 